  "text": "UIOs allow for state estimation even in the presence of unknown inputs (see, for instance, [CITATION_1] ). This is a particularly valuable feature in the case of DCmGs, as it allows DGU i to estimate the states of DGUs j, j ∈ N i , without requiring knowledge of their secondary input, exogenous inputs and of the states of their neighbors.",
